From: James Docherty <jamesdocherty97@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 10:51:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 5/6] Demo: partners auto-respond + one-tap demo from the
 config screen

- In demo mode, offers you send are accepted by the sample friend after a
  few seconds, and after you confirm a handover (or accept an offer) the
  partner confirms their side too - so a single device experiences the
  full loop: send offer, friend accepts, both confirm, books update.
  Production behaviour is untouched (all hooks are DEMO_MODE-only).
- 'App not configured' screen now has a real 'Try the demo' button
  instead of telling users to open quick-test.html by hand.
